V0708_01_00_00_0.text: I'm willing to Duel you - as long as it's a Rush Duel.

V0708_01_00_01_0.text: I am curious why you believe you have any chance to win.

V0708_01_00_02_0.text:
Your chance of winning isn't 0.001%.
It's 0%.

V0708_01_00_03_0.text: A deck is the source of infinite possibilities.

V0708_01_00_04_0.text: The universe was created so we'd be able to Duel.

V0708_01_00_05_0.text: Curiosity is the key to mastering all things.

V0708_01_00_06_0.text: Yuga, I wonder if your road actually leads to victory.

V0708_01_00_07_0.text: Only I can take what you created and improve upon it.

V0708_01_00_08_0.text: My curiosity led me to a revelation that's key to this Duel.

V0708_48_00_02_0.text: I'm curious to know what will happen in this Duel.

V0708_03_00_00_0.text: This Duel is going as I expected, and I won't change course.

V0708_03_00_01_0.text: With such few LP, you cannot win this Duel.

V0708_04_00_00_0.text: I'm curious to see what I draw!

V0708_03_00_04_0.text: I didn't expect you to play so well.

V0708_03_00_05_0.text: You're acting like you've won, but the Duel isn't over yet.

V0708_05_00_00_0.text: I see where this Duel is heading, but I won't accept it!

V0708_06_01_01_0.text: I'm curious why you did that.

V0708_07_09_00_0.text: You must have seen me Set this card earlier.

V0708_07_09_01_0.text: Did you forget about this card?

V0708_10_00_03_0.text: Now isn't the time for mercy.

V0708_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0708_14_00_02_0.text: A single battle can change the course of history.

V0708_16_00_00_0.text: Are you ready for your end?

V0708_21_00_00_0.text: You have no options other than to admit defeat.

V0708_21_00_01_0.text:
I admire your effort.
As ineffective as it is.

V0708_21_00_02_1.text: But this is the beginning of your end.

V0708_21_00_04_0.text: Your strategy has caught me by surprise.

V0708_21_00_05_0.text: I am learning much about how you Duel.

V0708_28_00_00_0.text: In an ever-changing world, you must always remain curious.

V0708_28_00_01_0.text: Have you asked yourself why things are the way they are?

V0708_28_00_01_1.text: You can't create the future if you don’t grasp the present.

V0708_28_00_02_0.text: In the whole scheme of the universe, you are worth nothing.

V0708_28_00_02_1.text: But even nothing can become something if they try.

V0708_28_00_03_0.text: I made Maximum Summon to go beyond the limits of Rush Duels.

V0708_28_00_04_0.text: It's time for you to go to sleep.

V0708_28_00_05_0.text: You were not strong enough to survive my Maximum Summons.

V0708_28_00_06_0.text:
You had excellent strategies.
But mine were better.

V0708_28_00_08_0.text: This Duel was no problem for someone with my capabilities.

V0708_28_00_09_0.text: Your heart couldn’t go past the limits you set for yourself.

V0708_28_00_10_0.text: I’m curious why you thought you even had a chance.

V0708_28_00_11_0.text: I'm curious why you thought your road would lead anywhere.

V0708_29_00_00_0.text: Thanks to you, I'm able to see a world of new possibilities.

V0708_29_00_01_0.text: There is great potential in your Duel - if you nurture it.

V0708_29_00_02_0.text:
I must admit...
That was fun.

V0708_29_00_04_0.text:
I'm surprised.
I've never played a Duel like this.

V0708_29_00_05_0.text: Owning the strongest cards doesn’t guarantee victory.

V0708_29_00_06_0.text: I'm curious to find out where your road leads.

V0708_29_00_07_0.text: The door to a new world has been opened - as Otes predicted.

V0708_29_00_08_0.text: Only you can turn a disadvantage into an advantage.

V0708_29_00_09_0.text: I learned today that no one can win on their own.

V0708_33_00_01_0.text: Your chances to win are zero.

V0708_33_00_02_0.text: You will never forget what you're about to see.

V0708_30_00_01_0.text: That goes against everything I believe.

V0708_30_00_02_0.text: There is no drawback in being curious.

V0708_34_00_01_0.text: You should not have done that!

V0708_34_00_02_0.text: I recommend that you do not play that card.

V0708_34_00_04_0.text: You've played too many cards defending against my attacks.

V0708_34_00_05_0.text: You're about to run out of cards in your deck.

V0708_34_00_06_0.text: Since you mistake deception for skill, you'll never beat me.

V0708_34_00_07_0.text: I didn't know you were so emotional.

V0708_34_00_08_0.text: You know why this is happening.

V0708_34_00_09_0.text: Allow me to erase the dark moments of your past.

V0708_34_00_10_0.text: In the end, we are all alone.

V0708_34_00_11_0.text:
Did you order delivery?
Here's your ramen!

V0708_32_00_01_0.text: I am curious to learn more about this Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links.

V0708_35_00_00_0.text:
My name is Nail.
I'm curious to see how you Duel.

V0708_35_00_01_0.text: I'm in charge of managing the Dueling network worldwide.

V0708_36_00_00_0.text: I leave the rest to you.

V0708_36_00_01_0.text: You should be the one to finish this Duel.

V0708_36_00_02_0.text: It was destiny for us to team together.

V0708_36_00_04_0.text: Do not let your opponent tempt you into making mistakes.

V0708_36_00_05_0.text: I am curious to see what you do to escape this situation.

V0708_36_00_08_0.text: Seatbastian, put them in their place.
